'''Memry Savanhu''' (nanone '''Memory Savanhu''' ) ni umukinnyi wa filime wa Nollywood wavukiye muri [[Zimbabwe]], Umukinnyi wa firime na  Rwiyemezamirimo, utuye burundu i Lagos, muri [[Nijeriya]] nyuma yo kwimurwa i Londere mu [[Ubwongereza|Bwongereza]] . Yatangiye bwa mbere muri filime, ''Intera Hagati'', mu 2008 <ref name="DB">https://www.nollywoodreinvented.com/2012/05/distance-between.html</ref> kandi kuva icyo gihe, yakinnye mu bintu byinshi bya Nollywood  ''One Fine Day'', <ref name="OFD">https://www.nollywoodreinvented.com/2016/05/one-fine-day.html</ref> ''On Bended Knees'' <ref name="OBK">https://www.nollywoodreinvented.com/2013/08/on-bended-knees.html</ref> na ''76'' . Niwe washinze Memkay Productions, imyambaro yo gutunganya film. <ref name="CW">http://www.daily-mail.co.zm/zambian-author-writes-zim-movie/</ref> <ref name="ZO">https://www.zimbabweonlinenews.com/local-film-premieres-in-uk/</ref> <ref name="NR">https://www.naijarules.com/threads/five-upcoming-actresses-to-look-out-for-in-2011.39345/</ref>

== Ubuzima n'uburere ==
Bivugwa ko Savanhu yavukiye muri [[Zimbabwe]] ''maze ahishurira ikinyamakuru Guardian'' cyo muri Nijeriya ko akomoka mu bwoko bwa Zezuru. Yize ikinamico i Londres no muri New York Film Academy i Abu Dhabi, [[Nyarabu Zunze Ubumwe|UAE]] yize gukora firime . <ref name="Guar">https://m.guardian.ng/guardian-woman/memry-savanhu-from-zimbabwe-with-love/</ref>

Muri 2015, yatorewe igihembo cya Zimbabwe International Women Awards (ZIWA) cyabereye i Birmingham mu [[Ubwongereza|Bwongereza]] mu Kwakira k'uwo mwaka nk'uko byatangajwe na ''The Herald'' of Zimbabwe. <ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/201509230871.html</ref> Iki gihembo ni icy'uruhare yagize muri Nollywood nk'uko ''Umudugudu w'Urubyiruko ubitangaza'' . <ref>https://youthvillage.co.zw/2015/09/zimbabwean-born-actress-memory-savanhu-makes-it-big-in-nollywood/</ref>

